          Title:  Simple, Accurate, Approximate Orbits in the Logarithmic
          and a Range of Power-Law Galactic Potentials
          Authors: Curtis Struck (Iowa State)
          Comments:  38  pages,  8  figures,  1  table,  accepted for the
