          In  this  paper,  we  present  a  first comparison of different
          Adaptive  Optics  (AO)  concepts  to  reach  a given scientific
          specification  for 3D spectroscopy on Extremely Large Telescope
          (ELT). We consider that a range of 30%-50% of Ensquarred Energy
          (EE)  in  H  band  (1.65um)  and in an aperture size from 25 to
