astro-ph/0601169 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Resolving the compact dusty discs around binary post-AGB
          stars using N-band interferometry
          Authors:  P. Deroo, H. Van Winckel, M. Min, L.B.F.M. Waters, T.
