          We  have  obtained  maps  of the large scale outflow associated
          with  the  UCHII  regionG5.89-0.39  in CO and 13CO (J=3-2), SiO
          (J=8-7,J=5-4),  SO2 (13(2,12)-13(1,13)) and H13CO+(J=4-3). From
