          Deep  Field South. Covering 992 sq. arcmin, this is the largest
          ``blank field'' surveyed for LAEs at z ~3, allowing an improved
          estimate  of the space density of this population of 3+-1x10^-4
          h_70^3/Mpc^3.  Spectroscopic follow-up of 23 candidates yielded
