astro-ph/0603313 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Why X-ray--Selected AGN Appear Optically Dull
          Authors: J. R. Rigby (1), G. H. Rieke (1), J. L. Donley (1), A.
          Alonso-Herrero  (2),  P.  G.  Prez-Gonzlez  (1)  ((1) Steward
          Observatory, (2) CSIC)
