astro-ph/0603592 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title:   Disk   Winds,  Jets,  and  Outflows:  Theoretical  and
          Computational Foundations
          Authors:  Ralph E. Pudritz, Rachid Ouyed, Christian Fendt, Axel
          Brandenburg
