          of  $\dot  P/P_{\rm  sh}  = -6.3(1.4) \times 10^{-5}$. However,
          detailed  analysis  of  the timings of superhump maxima seem to
          suggest  a  more  complex period change, with a decrease in the
          period  during  the  first and last stages of the superoutburst
