          have  weaker  Mgb5177  (at  ~8 sigma significance) and stronger
          Hbeta  and Hgamma absorption (~3 sigma, ~4 sigma) than galaxies
          of  the  same  velocity  dispersion  in  the cluster cores. The
          Fe5270  and  Fe5335  indices  show  only  very weak trends with
