astro-ph/0603718 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title: Structure of the hot object in the symbiotic prototype Z
          And during its 2000-03 active phase
          Authors:  A.  Skopal,  A.  Vittone,  L.  Errico,  M. Otsuka, S.
          Tamura, M. Wolf, V. Elkin
          Comments:  18  pages  (printed  format), 9 figures, 4 tables, 2
          appendices; accepted for publication in A&A (02/03/2006)
          Aims:  To  investigate  structure  of  the  hot  object  in the
          symbiotic  prototype  Z  And  during  its  major 2000-03 active
          phase.  Methods:  Analysis of the far ultraviolet, optical low-
          and   high-resolution   spectroscopy   and   UBVR   photometry.
