          the  outburst.  The  Raman  scattering process. Results: At the
          initial stages of the outburst the hot object was characterized
          by the two-temperature spectrum (a warm stellar radiation and a
          strong  nebular  emission) with signatures of a mass-outflow at
          moderate   (100-200   km/s)  and  very  high  (1000-2000  km/s)
