          Title: VW Hyi: optical spectroscopy and Doppler tomography
          Authors:  Amanda J. Smith (1), Carole A. Haswell (1), Robert I.
          Hynes  (2)  ((1)  The  Open  University,  (2)  Louisiana  State
          University)
