          even  very  strong  ones,  only  cause a small blueing of their
          intrinsically  blue  young  parent galaxies. At lower redshift,
          even   small  bursts  cause  a  significant  blueing  of  their
          intrinsically   redder  galaxies.  While  the  burst  phase  is
