          Authors:  Douglas  C. Heggie (Edinburgh), Simon Portegies Zwart
          (Amsterdam), Jarrod Hurley (Monash)
          Comments:  16 pages, Accepted for publication in New Astronomy.
          Source codes available at: this http URL and this http URL
          We  describe  a  simple  computer  package  which illustrates a
          method  of  combining  stellar dynamics with stellar evolution.
          Though  the  method  is  intended  for  elaborate  applications
          (especially  the  dynamical evolution of rich star clusters) it
          is  illustrated  here  in the context of three-body scattering,
