          reexamine the spectrum of the z = 0.087 elliptical radio galaxy
          PKS  0352-686,  the possible counterpart of the INTEGRAL source
          IGR  J03532-6829,  and  we  find  that it is a BL Lac. Physical
          parameters  for  these sources are also evaluated by discussing
          our  findings  in  the context of the available multiwavelength
