          Authors: S.L. Kenyon (1), J.S. Lawrence (1), M.C.B. Ashley (1),
          J.W.V.  Storey (1), A. Tokovinin (2), E. Fossat (3) ((1) School
          of  Physics,  University  of New South Wales, Sydney Australia,
