          Infrared   Diagnostics  of  Galaxy  Evolution,  Ed.  R.  Chary.
          November, 2005, Pasadena
          We  present  a preliminary investigation of the spectral energy
          distributions (SEDs), and star-formation properties of a sample
          of  Mid-IR  selected  Quasars.  The  mid-infrared  SEDs  of our
