astro-ph/0604597 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title:  Optical spectroscopy of (candidate) ultra-compact X-ray
          binaries: constraints on the composition of the donor stars
          Authors: G. Nelemans, P.G. Jonker, D. Steeghs
          Comments: Accepted for publication in MNRAS
          We   present   optical   spectroscopy  of  several  (candidate)
          ultra-compact  X-ray binaries (UCXBs) obtained with the ESO VLT
          and  Gemini-North telescopes. In only one of five observed UCXB
