          will  soon  be  possible  to  observe the neutral circumstellar
          medium directly involved in gas giant planet (GGP) formation at
          physical  scales  previously  unattainable. In order to explore
          possible  signatures  of  gas  giant  planet formation via disk
          instabilities,  we  have combined a 3D, non-local thermodynamic
          equilibrium  (LTE)  radiative  transfer  code with a 3D, finite
