          Aims:  Our goal is to set constraints on the evolutionary state
          of the dense core Cha-MMS1 in the Chamaeleon I molecular cloud.
          Methods:  We  analyze  molecular  line observations carried out
          with  the new submillimeter telescope APEX. We look for outflow
          signatures  around  the  dense  core  and  probe  its  chemical
          structure,  which  we  compare  to  predictions  of  models  of
          gas-phase  chemistry.  We  also  use the public database of the
