          formation   of  the  young  stellar  population  had  the  same
          underlying  cause,  this  source  provides  a  sequence for the
          events  surrounding the triggering process. We propose that the
          AGN  activity  in 9C J1503+4528 was causedby a relatively minor
          interaction,  and  that a super-massive black hole powering the
          radio  jets  must  have  been  in  place  before  the  AGN  was
          triggered.


   
