          We  present  the  first Spitzer Infrared Spectrograph (IRS; The
          IRS  was a collaborative venture between Cornell University and
          Ball  Aerospace  Corporation  funded  by  NASA  through the Jet
          Propulsion   Laboratory   and   the   Ames   Research  Center.)
