          We  present Australia Telescope Compact Array (ATCA) HI imaging
          of  the  edge-on  galaxy  NGC 1596, which was recently found to
          have counter-rotating ionized gas in its center (<15"). We find
          a  large  HI  envelope  associated with a nearby companion, the
          dwarf  irregular  galaxy  NGC  1602.  The  HI  covers  a region
