          Title:  New  perspectives  on  strong z=0.5 MgII absorbers: are
          halo-mass and equivalent width anti-correlated?
          Authors:  Nicolas  Bouche  (MPE,  Garching),  Michael T. Murphy
          (Institute   of  Astronomy,  Cambridge),  Celine  Peroux  (ESO,
