          Title: The Planets-Capture Model of V838 Monocerotis
          Authors:  Alon  Retter  (Penn  State  University),  Bing  Zhang
          (University  of  Nevada,  Las  Vegas), Lionel Siess (Universite
          Libre de Bruxelles), Amir Levinson (Tel Aviv University), Ariel
          Marom (Rafael Institute)
          Comments:  9  pages,  uses  asp2004.sty, an invited talk in the
