          Title: The compact circumstellar material around OH 231.8+4.2
          Authors:  M.  Matsuura,  O.  Chesneau, A.A. Zijlstra, W. Jaffe,
          L.B.F.M.  Waters,  J. Yates, E. Lagadec, T. Gledhill, S. Etoka,
