astro-ph/0607128 [abs, pdf] :
          Title: Many binaries among NEAs
          Authors: David Polishook, Noah Brosch
          Comments:   5  pages,  2  figures,  invited  paper  for  NASA's
          "Near-Earth  Object  Detection,  Characterization,  and  Threat
