          Title:  Eclipsing  binaries suitable for distance determination
          in the Andromeda galaxy
          Authors:  F. Vilardell (1), I. Ribas (2 and 3), C. Jordi (1 and
          3)  ((1)  Universitat de Barcelona, (2) Institut de Ciencies de
