          Title: Emission-line Diagnostics of Low Metallicity AGN
          Authors:  Brent  Groves  (1),  Timothy  Heckman  (2), Guinevere
          Kauffmann  (1)  ((1) MPA, Garching, Germany (2) JHU, Baltimore,
          MD, USA)
