          Aims:  To  model  broad  H-alpha  wings  observed  in symbiotic
          binaries  by an optically thin, bipolar stellar wind from their
          hot  components as an alternative to that considering the Raman
          scattering  of  Ly-beta  photons  on  atomic hydrogen. Methods:
