astro-ph/0607477 [abs, ps, pdf, other] :
          Title:  Radio  bubbles  in  the  composite AGN-starburst galaxy
          NGC6764
          Authors:  Ananda  Hota  (1,2),  D.J. Saikia (2) ((1) JAP, IISc,
