          stellar  system  capable  of  substantially  enriching  the gas
          metallicity  through  sustained star formation. We suggest that
          NGC  7742 cannibalised a smaller galaxy rich in metal-poor gas,
          and  that  star  formation  episodes  in  the  ring  have since
