          Seyfert  1  galaxy  Ark  564 and combine it with the month-long
          monitoring  of  the  same source produced by ASCA, to calculate
          the  phase  lags  and coherence between different energy bands,
          over  frequencies  ~  10^{-6} to 10^{-3} Hz. This is the widest
