          Authors:  Dana I. Casetti-Dinescu, Steven R. Majewski, Terrence
          M.  Girard,  Jefferey L. Carlin, William F. van Altena, Richard
          J. Patterson, David R. Law
          Comments: Accepter for publication in the Astronomical Journal
