          Kauffmann  (MPIfR),  Yancy  L.  Shirley  (Steward Obs), Antonio
          Crapsi  (Leiden),  Chadwick H. Young (Nicholls State), Tracy L.
          Huard  (CfA), Timothy Y. Brooke (Caltech), Nicholas Chapman (U.
