          SQUID  series  arrays. The first prototype detectors for CLOVER
          operate  with  a  bath  temperature  of  230 mK and are used to
          validate  the  detector  design  as  well  as  the  polarimeter
          technology.  We  describe  the  design of the CLOVER detectors,
          detector   blocks,   and   readout,   and  present  preliminary
          measurements of the prototype detectors performance.


   
