          measured  H(alpha)  and lithium equivalent widths. We have also
          estimated  their  effective temperature and gravity, which were
          used  to  produce  an  independent age estimation for these two
          brown  dwarfs.  We  have  also  collected  spectra of 2M1315, a
          candidate  member  with  a  L5  spectral  type and measured its
          H(alpha)   equivalent   width.   Our   age   estimate  for  the
          association,  10  Myr  (in  the  range  3-20  Myr), agrees with
