          We  have  redefined  group  membership  of  six southern galaxy
          groups in the local universe (mean cz < 2000 km/s) based on new
          redshift    measurements    from    our    recently    acquired
          Anglo-Australian  Telescope  2dF  spectra.  For  each group, we
