          low   mass   X-ray  binary  4U  1820-30  with  INTEGRAL  during
          2003-2005.  This  source  as  been  observed  in  both the soft
          (banana) and hard (island) spectral states. A high energy tail,
          above 50 keV, in the hard state has been observed for the first
          time.  This places the source in the category of X-ray bursters
